Add/Update stored path

places_add.Rd

Add or Update a stored path in the places object

.add(self, private, ...)

Arguments

self

places self object
private

places private object
…

named elements to store

See also

places

Examples

 dir <- places$new()
 dir
#> $root
#> [1] "/Users/yonis/projects/places"
#> 
#> $paths
#> list()
#> 
 dir$add(back = '..',this='.')
 dir
#> $root
#> [1] "/Users/yonis/projects/places"
#> 
#> $paths
#> $paths$back
#> [1] "/Users/yonis/projects"
#> 
#> $paths$this
#> [1] "/Users/yonis/projects/places"
#> 
#> 
 dir$names()
#> [1] "back" "this"
